        "cover": [
            {
                "id": "67",
                "title": "茂名职业技术学院首届“龙健杯”纪念品创意设计大赛评选晚会",
                "describe": "测试",
                "content": "<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 24px;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 28px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190517/1558063068.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 24px;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 28px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">茂名职业技术学院首届“龙健杯”纪念品创意设计大赛评选晚会于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">10</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">21</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">日在南校区教学楼</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">1</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">栋</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">201</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">举行。本次大赛由龙健集团总冠名，茂名职业技术学院学生处主办，计算机工程系团委承办，茂名职业技术学院学生助理团、易班发展中心、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">BIM</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">协会、计算机协会、建筑设计协会、书香协会协办。计算机工程系主任周洁文、化学工程系实训室主任陈颖峰、学生处综合科科长梁标、计算机工程系辅导员梁燕出席本次大赛。还邀请到何铮、陈思名、周丽莎、廖欣南、梁智五位评委老师。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 24px;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 28px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">龙健集团是全球最专业聚焦音视频的行业，一个集音乐、文化领域产业及研发、制造、销售、服务、文化传播、个人体验、培训等一体多元化发展的高新科技集团公司，旗下拥有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">30</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">家子公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">,100</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">多项技术专利。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 24px;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 28px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">本次大赛自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">2018</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">6</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">月启动，共收到学院各系同学投稿</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">169</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">份作品，分为吉祥物工艺品类、电器类、生活用品类、平面设计类，办公学习用品类。经过企业和学院多位专业老师的评审，分别选出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">30</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">份入围作品和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">13</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">份决赛作品，同时通过网络投票评选出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">1</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">名最具创意奖和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">1</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">名最具人气奖。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 24px;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 28px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">入选决赛的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">13</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\">份作品中，不乏许多优秀作品，学院下一步会将部分作品加工为实物成品，作为代表学院和企业的纪念品。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 24px;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 28px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 24px;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 28px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit\">入围选手名单如下：</strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 24px;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 28px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: inherit\"><br/></strong></span></p><table><tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box\"><tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box\" class=\"firstRow\"><td width=\"95\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0p